  ],
  "remarks": "Prominent company operating across multiple sectors of the Syrian economy. By facilitating fuel, arms and ammunition trade between the former al-Assad regime and various actors including ISIL (Da’esh) under the pretext of importing and exporting food items, supporting militias fighting alongside the former al-Assad regime and taking advantage of its ties with the former al-Assad regime to expand its commercial activity, Al Qatarji Company – whose board is headed by designated person Hussam Al Qatarji, a member of the Syrian People’s Assembly – supports and benefits from the former al-Assad regime.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}